snippet.title: Amber Heard & Johnny Depp Legal Battle: A Few More Thoughts From An Attorney (Full Video Out Soon)
snippet.description:
Amber Heard / Johnny Depp / Legal Analysis / 


This is another set of clips from my interview with attorney Andrea Burkhart. We talked for over an hour about the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard legal battle. I'm still editing the full interview, but it will be out asap this week. This short video here gives you a taste of the full 1-hour interview, so subscribe to my channel for the full interview and other videos on the Amber Heard and Johnny Depp situation as well as other celebrity topics. 


Please support me on Patreon and Paypal. This work takes time, energy, and money.
